                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-816-18610923 t18610923-816-punishment-74"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The Sergeant stated that the prisoner's character in the regiment was bad.</hi>
